Directions

The All Animal Expo is held at the DuPage County Fairgrounds located at 2015 Manchester Road in Wheaton, IL. The map above is where we are located and some helpful directions depending on which direction you may be coming from are below.
Dupage County Fairgrounds

 
LOCAL/EAST/WEST
Route 38 (Roosevelt) to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds

FROM NORTH
Route 59 South, Route 38 East to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds or Route 53 Exit, Route 38 West to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds

FROM SOUTH
Route 59 North, Route 38 East to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds or Route 53 North, Route 38 West to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds or I-355 North to Route 38 Exit, Route 38 West to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds

FROM I-88 (East/West Tollway)
From East or West, Take Winfield Road Exit, North on Winfield Road to Route 38, East to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds

FROM CHICAGO
Take I-290 (Eisenhower) to I-88 West, Take Winfield Road Exit, North on Winfield Road to Route 38, East to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds

FROM I-294
Take I-88 West, Take Winfield Road Exit, North on Winfield Road to Route 38, East to County Farm Road, North to Manchester, East to Fairgrounds
